rComments: Course isn't necessarily "easy", but it isn't hard either, just as long as you do your readings and study! Her tests aren't easy either, but they are fair. Some MCQ are little details from the textbook but that's only a bit of your mark so although it might be hard to get perfect, still can get a 4.0! Good prof!!

She's a good prof and her tests are fair, but she makes it hard to get a good mark unless you have no life. Class average for the 1st test was 57%. The exam is cumulative and that is A LOT of material you need to know.
reasonable prof. super helpful and approachable. tests are fair.
